                <p>Of course, the real fun starts when you get to the Free Spins feature. With tripled payouts, there's a lot of money to be won here. We're talking sums of thirty to fifty times your bet, which can add up quickly. Of course, not every spin will be a winner, but you'll definitely have a good time trying!</p>
